{"tid":1857161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到底醫護人員仲要受幾多不公平對待","createTime":"2020-02-02T05:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T05:38:03.000Z","uid":50912,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f81c5ff870ad39554ec564833890294e6f56956","tid":1857161,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:05:17.000Z","msg":"先唔提workload，工時，cut開支，減人手<br />\n講班醫護假如唔好彩真係殉左職<br />\n咁醫護人員呢？佢地可以得到啲咩？<br />\n黑警 「殉職 」可以著裝浩園， 死咗呢就政府養全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護人員得到：<br />\n一畢錢，一畢底薪*12倍既錢<br />\n然後，<br />\ndllm仲要係扣完強積金先賠<br />\n簡單啲尼講即係對沖<br />\n你死左之後賠比你啲錢仲要自己賠返錢賠比自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*重要唔知你係咪因公殉職所以唔知批唔撚批比你</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，唔生唔死個啲係冇人會理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下線先喺病房做嗰啲阿姐， 犧牲咗自己可以點呀！ 啲姑娘咁後生犧牲咗自己點呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n*份合約由03年沿用至今，個政府一直都冇進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ynd34oi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnd34oi.jpg&h=9f4cfb26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"054a06b71995c02ef9fe03f65d5503bb9846648e","tid":1857161,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"086aa8dd1bf992168445dde088e581932edf8c57","tid":1857161,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f87b578e06555c9b8439b8c37466e4da7b3facc3","tid":1857161,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:23:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1f6782613d67045ea9631e9db699710370af5469","tid":1857161,"uid":50912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"